---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure | Top AI Girlfriend Apps">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content glass-card">
        <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 27, 2024</p>
        
        <div class="disclosure-highlight">
          <p><strong>Important:</strong> TopAIGirlfriendApps.com is a participant in affiliate programs. We earn commissions from qualifying purchases made through links on this website.</p>
        </div>

        <section>
          <h2>What This Means for You</h2>
          <p>When you click on links to AI girlfriend apps on our website and make a purchase or sign up for a subscription, we may receive a commission from that company. This is how we fund our website and continue to provide free content and reviews.</p>
          <p><strong>This does not affect the price you pay.</strong> You pay the same amount whether you use our affiliate link or go directly to the website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>FTC Compliance</h2>
          <p>In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's 16 CFR Part 255 guidelines concerning the use of endorsements and testimonials in advertising, we want to be transparent about our affiliate relationships.</p>
          <p>We are required to disclose that we may receive compensation for products and services recommended on this website. This disclosure is provided for your protection and is intended to ensure full transparency.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Our Review Process</h2>
          <p>Despite our affiliate relationships, our reviews are honest and unbiased. Here's our commitment to you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Honest Reviews:</strong> Our reviews reflect our genuine opinions based on research and testing</li>
            <li><strong>No Pay-for-Play:</strong> Companies cannot pay for favorable reviews or higher rankings</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We clearly mark all affiliate links on our site</li>
            <li><strong>User First:</strong> Our primary goal is to help you find the right AI companion app</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Affiliate Programs We Participate In</h2>
          <p>We may be affiliates of the following types of programs:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Direct affiliate programs with AI girlfriend app companies</li>
            <li>Affiliate networks that connect us with various AI applications</li>
            <li>Referral programs offered by the reviewed platforms</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>How Affiliate Links Work</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>You click on a link to an AI girlfriend app on our website</li>
            <li>A cookie is placed on your browser to track the referral</li>
            <li>If you make a purchase within the cookie duration period, we earn a commission</li>
            <li>You pay the normal price - our commission comes from the company, not you</li>
          </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Your Privacy</h2>
          <p>Affiliate tracking cookies are used solely to attribute referrals and do not collect personal information. For more details about how we handle your data, please see our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Support Our Work</h2>
          <p>If you find our reviews helpful, using our affiliate links is a great way to support our continued work at no extra cost to you. However, you're never obligated to use our links - we appreciate your readership regardless!</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>Questions?</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions about our affiliate relationships or this disclosure, please don't hesitate to <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-4xl)) 0 var(--space-4xl);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
  }
  
  .legal-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }
  
  .last-updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .disclosure-highlight {
    background: #1e131a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 157, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .disclosure-highlight p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .legal-content section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  .legal-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
  
  .legal-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .legal-content ul, 
  .legal-content ol {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-left: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--color-accent-pink);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
